            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Radiochemical study of the 209Bi(p,7Be)203Hg process",
                " from 20 to 70 MeV via identification of the emitted",
                " particle (7Be) and the product nucleus (203Hg)"
